*Čuo* sam da će biti lepog vremena (I heard that the weather will be nice). 

Ona je *čula* da je njena sestra zaposlena (She heard that her sister was hired).

Oni su *čuli* govor tamo daleko (They heard a speech far away).

*Čula* sam da će biti snega sutra (I heard that it will snow tomorrow).

Nismo *čuli* njegove reči (We didn't hear his words).

*Čuli* smo o njegovim uspesima (We heard about his successes).